{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_14_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 ミュージカルのオーディション",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、面白かった\n久しぶりに舞台を観たけど、ミュージカルはいいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.0762814839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ステージで歌って踊って……\nアイドルとは違うけど、ああいうのも憧れるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "チケットをくれたさくらちゃんに\nお礼を言わないといけないわね。そうだ、メッセで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.6534288408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "「さくらちゃん、チケットを譲ってくれてありがとう\nミュージカルとても面白かったわ」、と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 23.6534288408
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2479.904492500001,
          "startTime": 26.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4946.571159200002,
          "startTime": 28.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8086.571159199998,
          "startTime": 31.74
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 32.6000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "あら、もう返事が来たわ。ええと……「もらい物の\nチケットだったけど、楽しんでもらえて良かった」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8132436752,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3503.333333300006,
          "startTime": 36.77
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.947077656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "「いつか遙子ちゃんがミュージカルする姿も\n観てみたいな。きっと凄く似合うと思うんだ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_evening",
      "startTime": 52.9945830664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばサニピがデビューしてすぐ、私が\nミュージカルの劇団にスカウトされたことがあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333372754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は私がアイドルを辞めるんじゃないかって\nサニピのみんなが心配して、相談に乗ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9333372754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "結局アイドルの道を選んだけど、もしかしたら私が\nミュージカル俳優になっていた未来もあったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5666706087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.0729504269
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.0729504269
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 79.4096171698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　今度は{user}君からだわ\nええと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1457662694,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2490.382830200005,
          "startTime": 82.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.7524743241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "「遙子さんにミュージカルのオーディションの話が\nきたんですが、受けてみますか？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9333372754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "随分とタイムリーな話ね\n添付されたファイルがオーディションの資料かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6425.008535199993,
          "startTime": 99.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.2683241369
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.1666701001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、このミュージカル……。そう、再演するのね\n麻奈ちゃんが主役を演じた、あのミュージカルを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1666701001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈がデビューしてから半年後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0430636249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_evening",
      "startTime": 116.6430610818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……麻奈ちゃん、今のがオーディションの\n課題曲なんだけど、どうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2455163012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "とっても良かったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4630600454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これならオーディションもばっちりだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5000008902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう\n主演の麻奈ちゃんにそう言ってもらえると自信になるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8000008902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_think-05.m4a",
      "text": "主演と言っても、私もミュージカルは初めてだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.106890599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あんまり偉そうなことは言えないけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.7617029001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-15.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、私がミュージカルの主役だなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0298282147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "未だに信じられないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1384612559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわ。麻奈ちゃんの人気と実力なら\n大抜擢されても不思議じゃないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7666685741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "私も負けていられないわ。今度のオーディションで\n主人公の親友役を必ず射止めてみせるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2333352407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-03.m4a",
      "text": "やけに気合いが入ってるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.4693751811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子ちゃんってそんなにミュージカルが好きだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9870880577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳じゃないわ\n白状するとミュージカルもそこまで詳しい訳じゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3666624706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
