      "text": "それは……\nこのミュージカルの主役が麻奈ちゃんだからよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.7333291372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんはデビューしてすぐに人気が出たでしょ？\nかたや私は人気も知名度もない売れないアイドル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.8333343505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "普通にやっていたら、麻奈ちゃんと一緒の仕事なんて\n回って来ないわ",
